		<div class="leading">
		<div class="title"><h2><a href="http://www.restaurantlarivista.com/ristorante_la_rivista/information/wine__cheese_bar_la_rivista_poliedric_local.html">Wine & Cheese Bar La Rivista poliedric local</a></h2></div>
		<div class="text">
				<p>&quot;<strong>La Rivista wine &amp; cheese bar</strong>&quot; has a modern, fresh atmosphere where <strong>design</strong> features prominently. It is characterized by metal elements, like the old hat racks displayed on the walls. A few steps down from the entrance of <strong>La Rivista</strong> is a large marble and polychrome composition inspired by a cartoon for a floral piece by Fortunato Depero: with other artwork it forms part of the Serandrei family's art collection.</p><p>The bar itself is an original 1940s piece (salvaged from an old, hotel in neighbouring Padua, now long closed), and the bamboo flooring, dark-red leather sofas, glass, steel, and starlight tables, the lamps resembling inverted Neapolitan coffeepots and the Futurist-inspired staircase, all combine to form a look which is both modern and sophisticated. Regular customers are Venetians, always ready to appreciate innovation, and foreigners in search of the perfect blend of <strong>Venice</strong>, art and design, and of course all those who love good food and value quality.</p><p>our <strong>Venice&nbsp;wine &amp; cheese bar</strong>&nbsp;offers&nbsp;drinks, snacks,&nbsp;assorted cheese boards and cold cuts&nbsp;of local and international inspiration, all in a modern Design ambience.</p>				</div>
	</div>
